_sText:
Outstanding isometric style map 

Features
-town style theme
-Ergonomic gameplay
-detailed buildings
-small to medium sized map
-custom textures
-Soundscapes (underground and above)
-3d skybox
-Areaportals
-Nodraw textures for the outside (obviously)
-parralax textures (advanced bump mapping for shadows)
-General store, Restaurant, cleaners, construction site, warehouse, port, underground tunnels
-48 player spawns
-spot lighting 
-realistic glow lighting
